                     <interp inst="t18231022-15-person191" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was servant to a grocer, but am out of place. I was walking with Mr. Watson, and saw the prisoner take the handkerchief from his pocket - I followed him, and saw him drop it; he ran through a public-house - I pursued, and never lost sight of him. An officer came up, and took him.</p>

               <p>Prisoner. I beg for mercy.</p>
